{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-24","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 24","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nakon neuređene liste, dodaj novu sliku sa vrednošću atributa elementa <code>src</code> postavljeno na:</p>\n<p><code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg</code></p>\n<p>I vrednost svojstva elementa <code>alt</code> je:</p>\n<p><code>A slice of lasagna on a plate.</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5dfb6250eacea3f48c6300b2","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-24"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        \n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[13,20],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Dodaj element <code>img</code> odmah posle završne oznake <code>&#x3C;/ul></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1].querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.nodeName, 'IMG');"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika nema atribut polja <code>alt</code>. Uverite se da postoji razmak nakon imena oznake otvaranja i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa polja.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1].querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.hasAttribute('alt'));"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika mora imati vrednost od <code>alt</code> od <code>A slice of lasagna on a plate.</code>. Proverite da je vrednost svojstva elementa <code>alt</code> okružena navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\n  document.querySelectorAll('section')[1].querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('alt')?.replace(/\\s+/g, ' '), /^A slice of lasagna on a plate\\.?$/i \n);"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika nema atribut elementa <code>src</code>. Uverite se da postoji razmak nakon naziva otvarajuće oznake i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa elemenata.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1].querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.hasAttribute('src'));"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika treba da ima vrednost atributa <code>src</code> jednaku <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg</code>. Uverite se da je vrednost atributa <code>src</code> stavljena pod navodnike.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(\n  document.querySelectorAll('section')[1].querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('src'),\n    'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg'\n);"},{"text":"<p>Iako si postavio atribut <code>src</code> nove slike na ispravan URL, preporučuje se da vrednosti atributa uvek budu pod navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(!/\\<img\\s+.+\\s+src\\s*=\\s*https:\\/\\/cdn\\.freecodecamp\\.org\\/curriculum\\/cat-photo-app\\/lasagna\\.jpg/.test(code));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-24","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-25","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-23","id":"5dfb6250eacea3f48c6300b2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-24"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}